title: Khloe K rocks new hairdo
text: Monday, 26 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) *Washington D.C., Oct.26 (ANI): Khloe Kardashian seems to have impressed everyone with her new hairdo.* Washington D.C., Oct.26 (ANI): Khloe Kardashian seems to have impressed everyone with her new hairdo. The 31-year-old TV personality, who has always rocked long, layered locks, was recently spotted with chopped hair at Kim Kardashian 's baby shower, E! Online reports. Confirming the news of Khloe's new hair style, her pal Malika Haqq shared a selfie collage of the two on her Twitter page and captioned it as, "Short hair don't care." The pic shows the 'Keeping Up with the Kardashians' star rocking her new tresses just below the tops of her shoulders, which is said to be at least six inches shorter than before. (ANI)
